OL,3,CMoD issued with Crown censure over
OL,4,Csoldier's death on training exercise
OL,6,FThe Ministry of Defence has been
OL,7,Fcensured with the maximum sanction
OL,8,Ffrom the Health and Safety Executive
OL,9,Ffollowing the death of a soldier who
OL,10,Fwas accidentally shot during a night-
OL,11,Ftime training exercise.
OL,13,FConor McPherson, a private in the
OL,14,FBlack Watch, 3rd Battalion, the Royal
OL,15,FRegiment of Scotland, died while
OL,16,Ftraining at the Heely Dod firing range
OL,17,Fin Otterburn, Northumberland, on 22
OL,18,FAugust 2016.
