OL,3,CMoD issued with Crown censure over
OL,4,Csoldier's death on training exercise
OL,6,FHis father described him as a "model
OL,7,Fson" and said the family have been
OL,8,Fleft facing a future of "deep sorrow".
OL,10,FThe Health and Safety Executive (HSE)
OL,11,Fsaid Pte McPherson was part of a team
OL,12,Fof five when he was accidentally shot
OL,13,Fin the back of the head by a fellow
OL,14,Fsoldier at around 11pm.
OL,16,FThe 24-year-old, from Paisley, died at
OL,17,Fthe scene.
