OL,4,Csoldier's death on training exercise
OL,6,FThe group had been shooting at remote
OL,7,Fcontrolled targets as they manoeuvred
OL,8,Fon foot through the moorland firing
OL,9,Frange and were using live rounds and
OL,10,Fnight vision technology at the time.
OL,12,FAn HSE investigation found the MoD
OL,13,F(Army) failed to properly implement a
OL,14,Fsafe system of work for the exercise.
OL,16,FIt has issued the MoD with a Crown
OL,17,Fcensure and said by accepting the
OL,18,Fcensure, the MoD admitted breaching
OL,19,Fhealth and safety at work rules.
