OL,6,FHSE inspector Jonathan Wills said:
OL,7,F"Our thoughts are with the family of
OL,8,FPrivate McPherson, with whom we have
OL,9,Fremained in close contact.
OL,11,F"Just like any other employer, the MoD
OL,12,Fhas a responsibility to reduce dangers
OL,13,Fto its personnel, as far as it
OL,14,Fproperly can."
OL,16,FThe HSE investigation found the
OL,17,Fplanning and conduct of the exercise
OL,18,Fwere poor, with an ineffective system
OL,19,Fto monitor the management arrangements
OL,20,Fmandated within the MoD's own
OL,21,Fprocedures.
