OL,6,FOfficers who were not sufficiently
OL,7,Fexperienced in controlling such an
OL,8,Factivity and were not properly
OL,9,Fmentored or supervised to deal with an
OL,10,Fexercise of such complexity, HSE said.
OL,12,F'The future is one of deep sorrow'
OL,14,FNeil McPherson, Conor's father, said
OL,15,Fthe family are still struggling to
OL,16,Fcome to terms with his death.
