OL,6,FIn his victim personal statement, he
OL,7,Fsaid: "Conor was a model son. He did
OL,8,Fnot drink or smoke and he loved his
OL,9,Ffamily life. He loved books and his PC
OL,10,Fgames and Saturday night films on TV.
OL,12,F"On the night Conor died, it was every
OL,13,Fparent's worst nightmare. A knock at
OL,14,Fthe door, two men in suits bearing
OL,15,Fnews that we had lost our son. I think
OL,16,Fwe both went into shock but the
OL,17,Fmemories of it all are blurred.
OL,26,@oD@GOUtD@AOU
