OL,6,F"Betty and I have many pictures that
OL,7,Fto date I cannot bear to look at,
OL,8,Falthough we often reminisce together.
OL,9,FWe also both have one of Conor's dog
OL,10,Ftags each which we wear on a chain."
OL,12,FThe MoD cannot face prosecution in the
OL,13,Fsame way as non-Government bodies and
OL,14,Fa Crown censure is the maximum
OL,15,Fsanction for a Government body that
OL,16,FHSE can bring.
