OL,3,CMoD issued with Crown censure over
OL,4,Csoldier's death on training exercise
OL,6,FThere is no financial penalty
OL,7,Fassociated with Crown censure, but
OL,8,Fonce accepted is an official record of
OL,9,Fa failing to meet the standards set
OL,10,Fout in law.
OL,12,FThe Crown censure was accepted by the
OL,13,FBritish Army. Lieutenant General Dame
OL,14,FSharon Nesmith DCB Deputy Chief of the
OL,15,FGeneral Staff (DCGS), as the Army
OL,16,FSafety Champion said: "I, on behalf of
OL,17,Fthe Army, am deeply sorry for failing
OL,18,FPte Conor McPherson. I unreservedly
OL,19,Fapologise to his family for Conor's
OL,20,Ftragic death in a training accident on
OL,21,F22 August 2016.
OL,26,@xD@WOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/13
