OL,4,Csoldier's death on training exercise
OL,6,F"We 100 per cent accept the Health and
OL,7,FSafety Executive findings. We failed
OL,8,Fto plan, organise, control and monitor
OL,9,Fthe critical safety aspects of this
OL,10,Flive firing training event.
OL,12,F"Whilst live firing is complex and
OL,13,Frisky, Conor's death was preventable.
OL,14,FWe care hugely about our soldiers -
OL,15,Fabove all else their health and
OL,16,Fwellbeing - on this occasion we got it
OL,17,Fwrong. Very wrong.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
